001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007@HistoryLogProps(
008    opCode = 477,
009    displayName = "CGM Join Session (FSL3)",
010    internalName = "LID_CGM_JOIN_SESSION_FSL3"
011)
012public class CgmJoinSessionFsl3HistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
013
014    public CgmJoinSessionFsl3HistoryLog() {}
015    public CgmJoinSessionFsl3HistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum) {
016        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
017        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
018
019    }
020
021    public int typeId() {
022        return 477;
023    }
024
025    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
026        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
027        this.cargo = raw;
028        parseBase(raw);
029
030    }
031
032    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum) {
033        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
034            new byte[]{(byte) 477, 0},
035            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
036            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum)));
037    }
038}
